high_descs: Make a right around the countertop to walk to the coffee machine.
Pick up the mug from the coffee machine.
Turn to walk to the sink.
Wash the mug in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn to face the coffee machine.
Put the mug back on the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Wash a mug to put it back on the coffee machine.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the counter and walk to the coffee maker ahead.
Pick up the dirty mug from the platform of the coffee maker.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Put the dirty mug into the left side of the sink, rinse it, fill it with water and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk to the coffee maker on the left.
Put the clean mug with water on the platform of the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean mug with water on a coffee maker.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter then turn left and walk to the coffee maker.
Pick up the dirty mug that's in front of you under the coffee maker.
Move to your left until you face the sink.
Wash the mug in the right sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn right and walk to the counter then turn left.
Put the mug back where you got it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug under the coffee maker.
